{"tid":1485733,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日多謝你！香港好在有你！","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T05:09:14.000Z","uid":113148,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"682c9e44eb0521c156e326542f53049c1d687a26","tid":1485733,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">dllm唔係你呀mon po 狗！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日真係好辛苦，兩點幾開始落大雨，都影響唔到香港人出黎既堅持、決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">多謝今日每一個用腳行左好耐，不論係咪入到維園既~200萬香港人！</span></strong></span>政府話我地暴民？我地818用和平既民意，對準政權，<ins>大大力錫9政府春</ins>袋！dllm 只有暴政！<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">多謝文宣用力推818、搞放映會</span></span></strong>，唔同地方連儂牆，俾人撕完又撕，過幾日你地又去貼大大張彩色文宣落去！好多老中青都會企定定喺度睇！<ins>遍地開花好！重！要！</ins><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">多謝啱啱旗手，同現場手足退落天橋，真係好撚型，差dj出血</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有好多手足都唔係靜靜雞走，而係<ins>一路走一路浪費口水，冒住被潑冷水既風險</ins>咁提埋其他人！好偉大！ (p.s.成日都喺度食花生個d，記得唔好要人擔心啦，個個都好緊張每位手足，真係會瞓唔到覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，民陣報左今日有超過170萬人(-6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ，仲未計好多捱唔到入維園既人。<br />\n<br />\n聽日，我地要見到報紙頭條，係170萬人和平集<strong>會呀CLS！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今晚唔要見到有狗呀！有得佢地on99 等落更啦！黑警死全家呀dllm！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝你，香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五大訴求，決一不可！<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 永不忘記 追究到底</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsKyAka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsKyAka.jpg&h=f9a71e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映: 罷買罷食。消費有得揀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeChyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxeChyA.jpg&h=eda39a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4d3c77911d3eee1eaa55b934c25eee51acca3c3","tid":1485733,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">【雨傘2.0】劉業成有心公開銅鑼灣班卧底 就係想大家一齊捉鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481711</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">認清楚係咪警察計謀 再決定點做<br />\n唔該手足</span>"},{"pid":"e54cf1ab378b8dc7e2502f56041c2574c955b4ab","tid":1485733,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"mon po suck my dick"},{"pid":"7a447e078dcb989c4c7c88ec3e59c3f81bed9cab","tid":1485733,"uid":120084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"多謝晒大家！令我感覺到香港仲有希望"},{"pid":"3299532aaeb58ba1b68c63df1e73277160bb1bd1","tid":1485733,"uid":73785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"今日係咪都係零被捕？ <br />\n<br />\nBtw 慶幸見到個正面既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bc25607adc30bd4cdcd504faa20a8bc97327a5","tid":1485733,"uid":224857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒咁多位，特別係老一輩同10幾歲新一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時15：11。我影完天下一秒就落大雨，個個淋濕晒有遮都濕。<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"45b6cbfe114f3dc6059a0eef811610db1c31fe2b","tid":1485733,"uid":113148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"682c9e44eb0521c156e326542f53049c1d687a26","tid":1485733,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">dllm唔係你呀